UID:69f0fAz3LGAQQq2ufnTdq
SUMMARY:Occidental Square Trading Post
DTSTAMP:20260406T054307Z
DTSTART:20260425T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Occidental Square Trading Post returns for 2026! This outdo
	or Saturday market in the heart of historic Pioneer Square features local 
	vendors selling handmade\, antique and vintage goods. Watch out for update
	s on Instagram. The market will pop up in Occidental Square on the followi
	ng dates from noon-6 p.m.:\n\nApril 25\nMay 30\nSept. 12\nOct. 17\nDec. 12
	\n\n\n\nEvent image: https://downtownseattle.org/app/uploads/2025/09/event
	s-occ-market-2025.jpg\n\nhttps://downtownseattle.org/event/occidental-squa
	re-trading-post/2026-04-25/
URL:https://downtownseattle.org/event/occidental-square-trading-post/2026-0
	4-25/
LOCATION:Occidental Square\, 117 S Washington St.\, Seattle\, WA undefined
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT6H
END:VEVENT
